extras.optText:
##### Youtube Video Stats How-To 

This template uses *Browser* and *Function* nodes to extract video stats from
a Youtube video.

Follow these steps to test this template;

**1.** Edit the Config Node

**2.** Set the msg.url field to the URL of the Youtube video you want to extract
stats.
